  * Right column: 4 cols (Insights, rights, stories)
* **Mobile:** All sections stack, 1 column; order: Hero â†’ Your Area â†’ Recent Activity â†’ Fresh Answers â†’ What People Are Asking â†’ Departments â†’ Insights â†’ High Impact â†’ Rights â†’ Toolkit â†’ Spotlight â†’ Browse by Topic â†’ Footer.

